{"tid":2322490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血時報：全民防疫　港人自救　「全民戴口罩」行動","createTime":"2020-12-12T11:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T11:23:15.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c44faa87b34cee9ba14104400594baf7f8d00483","tid":2322490,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkBC6Xf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkBC6Xf.jpg&h=35420cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Va-I2qAs474/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FVa-I2qAs474%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=9ff81de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱血編輯部：<br />\n踏入2015 年1 月流感爆發，直至2 月10 日中午為至，已經有224 宗流感嚴重、需入住深切治療部的個案，其中236 宗為H3N2 確診病例，死亡人數達157 人。雖然政府稱今年流感整體死亡率低於1％，但是病情嚴重患者的死亡率已達3.5％，而深切治療部病人的死亡率更超過一半。<br />\n然而，在每日流感死亡人數維持最少8 至10 人、疫情日趨嚴重的情況下，香港政府反應緩慢、後知後覺，更被社會輿論質疑高官有否忍暪疫情，又批評政府刻意冷處理流感肆虐。面對人心惶惶，熱血公民和不少熱心市民自發發起免費派發口罩行動，並在人流較多的地方開設街站，宣傳提防流感，以及注重公共衛生的訊息，有網民更計劃在各區自組小隊全民對抗疫。毫無疑問，政府冷漠、特首傲慢，和官僚麻目，正是流感疫情導致上百港人死亡的主因，為什麼H3N2 的死亡人數直迫03 年「沙士」，政府仍然無動於衷？當中除了害怕影響經濟和樓市的因素外，到底還有什麼政治考慮呢？"},{"pid":"e2e44cd05c64a5943dd33cf3b0e110b9cef0ff02","tid":2322490,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"醫科生怒屌熱狗日日係到Just the flu<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2322245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2322245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8149e7e2026d4f7496294a8472fc4d84f01032d","tid":2322490,"uid":38164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">尻</span>"},{"pid":"99640b828347133f8ba77493183a7aae0c0e1eae","tid":2322490,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c84b229eab18df769fc7551d92a6e612b16dcc","tid":2322490,"uid":28962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}